---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Verkada Command Connector | Blue Cap IT — Gold Partner" description="Verkada Command Connector integrates third-party and legacy cameras into the Verkada Command platform. Blue Cap IT is a Verkada Gold Partner. Call (410) 858-4031.">
  <div class="inner-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="verkada.html">Verkada Solutions</a> <span>/</span> Command Connector</div>
      <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;align-items:center;">
        <div>
          <div class="section-label">Verkada Solution</div>
          <h1>Verkada <span class="grad">Command Connector</span></h1>
          <p class="section-sub">Bring your existing cameras into the Verkada cloud. Command Connector is Verkada's on-premise appliance that integrates third-party, ONVIF-compatible cameras into the Verkada Command platform — so you can keep your current investment while gaining modern cloud management.</p>
          <div style="margin-top:2rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Get a Quote</a>
            <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost btn-sm">📞 (410) 858-4031</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img src="/command-connector-hero.png" alt="Verkada Command Connector appliance" style="width:100%;border-radius:1rem;" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="feature-list">
        <div class="feature-row">
          <div class="feature-visual"><div class="feature-visual-bg"></div><div class="big-icon">🔗</div></div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Integrate Third-Party Cameras into Verkada Command</h3>
            <p>Command Connector is Verkada's on-premise appliance that bridges the gap between legacy camera systems and the Verkada cloud platform. Connect non-Verkada cameras and manage them alongside native Verkada devices in a single dashboard.</p>
            <ul class="feature-bullets">
              <li>Supports ONVIF-compatible cameras from any manufacturer</li>
              <li>View third-party feeds directly in Verkada Command</li>
              <li>Unified management for both Verkada and non-Verkada cameras</li>
              <li>No need to rip and replace your existing camera infrastructure</li>
              <li>Gradual migration path to a full Verkada deployment</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-row rev">
          <div class="feature-visual"><div class="feature-visual-bg"></div><div class="big-icon">🧠</div></div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>AI Analytics on Any Camera</h3>
            <p>Unlock Verkada's powerful AI-driven analytics on your existing camera feeds. Command Connector applies the same intelligent video processing used on native Verkada cameras to your third-party devices.</p>
            <ul class="feature-bullets">
              <li>Person and vehicle detection on third-party camera feeds</li>
              <li>Searchable video history with smart filters</li>
              <li>Motion-based alerts and notifications</li>
              <li>Object tracking across connected cameras</li>
              <li>Same AI capabilities as native Verkada cameras</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-row">
          <div class="feature-visual"><div class="feature-visual-bg"></div><div class="big-icon">💾</div></div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Local Storage &amp; Cloud Connectivity</h3>
            <p>Command Connector provides on-site storage for your third-party camera footage while maintaining cloud connectivity to Verkada Command. Video is stored locally and accessible remotely — no separate NVR required.</p>
            <ul class="feature-bullets">
              <li>On-board storage for third-party camera recordings</li>
              <li>Cloud-managed with remote access from anywhere</li>
              <li>Eliminates the need for standalone NVRs or DVRs</li>
              <li>Automatic health monitoring and status alerts</li>
              <li>End-to-end encryption for all video data</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-row rev">
          <div class="feature-visual"><div class="feature-visual-bg"></div><div class="big-icon">🏢</div></div>
          <div class="feature-content">
            <h3>Protect Your Existing Camera Investment</h3>
            <p>Organizations with hundreds or thousands of legacy cameras don't need to replace everything overnight. Command Connector lets you bring those cameras into Verkada Command today and transition to native Verkada hardware on your own timeline.</p>
            <ul class="feature-bullets">
              <li>Keep existing cameras from Axis, Hikvision, Dahua, Hanwha, and more</li>
              <li>Reduce upfront costs by leveraging current infrastructure</li>
              <li>Centralized management across all sites and camera types</li>
              <li>Phased migration strategy with no disruption to operations</li>
              <li>Full Verkada Command features for every connected camera</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="section-inner" style="text-align:center;max-width:800px;">
      <div class="section-label">Hardware</div>
      <h2>Command Connector <span class="grad">Appliance</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">The Command Connector is a compact, rack-mountable appliance designed for easy deployment. It connects to your network, discovers ONVIF-compatible cameras, and streams them into Verkada Command with minimal configuration. Available in multiple models to match your camera count and storage requirements.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="cta-band">
    <div class="section-label">Ready to Unify Your Camera System?</div>
    <h2>Bring Your Cameras into<br/><span class="grad">Verkada Command</span></h2>
    <p>Blue Cap IT will assess your current camera infrastructure and show you how Command Connector can bring everything into one platform. Get a free consultation today.</p>
    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="contact.html" class="btn-primary">Schedule a Consultation</a>
      <a href="tel:4108584031" class="btn-ghost">📞 (410) 858-4031</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@bluecapit.com" class="btn-ghost">✉️ info@bluecapit.com</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
